  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">A Life of Worry: Politics, Mental Health, and Vietnam\u2019s Age of Anxiety (2023), published by University of California Press. Pedagogical anchor (strength 0.6). Scholarly uptake (strength 0.6).</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">A Life of Worry: Politics, Mental Health, and Vietnam\u2019s Age of Anxiety was published by University of California Press in 2023. Conceptually, the work connects to Prosperity, Worry, Ho chi minh, Politics and Anxiety.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">OpenAlex records 18 citations. Citations peaked in 2025 with 12 citing works. Notable citing venues include Anthropology and Medicine, Culture Medicine and Psychiatry and Anthropologica. Inferred role: Pedagogical anchor and Scholarly uptake.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Teaching use: 1 OCW. 5125 recorded downloads via open-access infrastructure.  SDG alignment: Decent work and economic growth.</p>",
